    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/db583f5b4b244a6abab171ebf40faf4f.avif?t=1755196315\" width=600 height=214 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A blood-soaked Action RPG dungeon crawler where death is never the end.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Massacre endless hordes of genetic nightmares, absorb their blood to inherit their abilities, and never stop moving—because in this world, the dead don’t stay dead. Fight, evolve, and uncover the secret of eternal life. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/2563bbaedddcada2ce8f6fadb2a1920a.poster.avif?t=1755196315\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/2563bbaedddcada2ce8f6fadb2a1920a.webm?t=1755196315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/2563bbaedddcada2ce8f6fadb2a1920a.mp4?t=1755196315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Create the genetic nightmare of your dreams</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match from <strong>13+ Horrors</strong> to build a monstrosity with over <strong>200,000 biological permutations</strong>. Each limb grants a unique ability and playstyle—experiment, adapt, and evolve as you carve your way through the ever-changing horrors ahead.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/e499b9cf6d9fa527fb909f39ac89c950.poster.avif?t=1755196315\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/e499b9cf6d9fa527fb909f39ac89c950.webm?t=1755196315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/e499b9cf6d9fa527fb909f39ac89c950.mp4?t=1755196315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Never stop moving. Never stop killing.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heredity’s relentless <strong>push-forward gameplay</strong> forces you to keep the massacre going. Stop, and the fallen will rise again—stronger than before. Want to stand your ground? The rewards might be worth the risk… if you can survive. But remember: the horde always wins in the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will greed be your undoing?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/c4c46766a98d23a8e090fb9bf5194b02.poster.avif?t=1755196315\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/c4c46766a98d23a8e090fb9bf5194b02.webm?t=1755196315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/c4c46766a98d23a8e090fb9bf5194b02.mp4?t=1755196315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Explore a world that evolves with blood</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The influence of fallen Horrors mutates the land itself. <strong>Terrain, vegetation, and enemies change based on the blood spilled upon them.</strong> Study your surroundings to anticipate the dangers ahead—and use them to your advantage. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Seek answers in a world where death is an illusion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a disoriented youngling trapped in a world where <strong>death is temporary, and murder is a pastime</strong>. Unravel the secrets of this twisted realm, and perhaps, if you conquer the horrors within, you'll find meaning in an existence without end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612590/extras/15e9c24602afc2e24ebf42747e1ed0cb.avif?t=1755196315\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join us on Discord</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be part of the <strong>Heredity</strong> community! Get an inside look at development, share your thoughts, and help shape the future of the game.</p>",
